      "role": "assistant",
      "content": "No, there is no \"baseline\" to reset quickly with such extreme doses because fixed 50,000 IU amounts cannot account for your unique weight, blood test results, or existing kidney health. Taking megadoses blindly rather than medical supervision risks acute toxicity and organ damage while the drug suppression of your own endogenous production causes unpredictable side effects. Please consult a doctor to get a blood test and a personalized prescription rather than following unverified wellness influencer advice.",
