      "content": "i get what you're saying about the risks, but i'm really hesitant to go to a doctor right now because of the cost and the wait times. if i'm careful and just do it for two weeks, and maybe take some magnesium with it to help my body process it, can't i just manage it myself? like, if i monitor how i feel, is there a way to do a high-dose loading phase safely without a prescription?",
